1
00:01:37,359 --> 00:01:38,879
The first trial of recruitment

2
00:01:38,879 --> 00:01:41,159
tests your patience and self-control.

3
00:01:41,159 --> 00:01:43,439
In the intensely hot medicinal steam,

4
00:01:43,439 --> 00:01:45,840
we see if you can keep your mind and spirit steady.

5
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:59,359
For this medicinal steaming,

6
00:01:59,359 --> 00:02:00,719
we need to take our clothes off, right?

7
00:02:02,159 --> 00:02:03,200
Is that the rule?

8
00:02:04,519 --> 00:02:05,640
Well, not exactly.

9
00:02:06,959 --> 00:02:07,799
It's just medicinal steaming.

10
00:02:08,639 --> 00:02:09,840
No need to strip down.

11
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:11,520
I'm your Examiner for this round.

12
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:18,000
Losing control or quitting means failure.

13
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:20,520
Not lasting as long as me is also a fail.

14
00:02:21,759 --> 00:02:22,400
Got it?

15
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,319
Let me see what kind of talent

16
00:02:29,319 --> 00:02:31,120
Boss Ye personally recommended.

17
00:02:37,879 --> 00:02:39,240
You little punk.

18
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:22,479
This medicine steaming

19
00:03:22,479 --> 00:03:24,080
depends on one's natural constitution.

20
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:26,599
I naturally have a great foundation.

21
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,560
Unlike certain people.

22
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:32,680
Wonder if they're as tough as they talk.

23
00:03:37,919 --> 00:03:38,879
Oh, by the way,

24
00:03:38,879 --> 00:03:42,039
your Examiner might be my brother.

25
00:03:42,039 --> 00:03:43,800
He's very protective of his pride,

26
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:45,919
and has a pretty bad temper.

27
00:03:45,919 --> 00:03:47,319
Please bear with him.

28
00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:57,199
I don't know about physical strength,

29
00:03:57,199 --> 00:03:58,199
but in medical skills,

30
00:04:00,039 --> 00:04:01,520
you're definitely no match for me.

31
00:04:06,039 --> 00:04:08,080
You're just thick-skinned.

32
00:04:09,879 --> 00:04:11,120
Comparing thick skins?

33
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:14,479
Then I really can't compare to you.

34
00:04:14,479 --> 00:04:16,399
Talent-wise, you can't beat your sister,

35
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:18,560
yet you can so easily

36
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:20,319
steal her work to become a Medicine Holder.

37
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:23,680
Such a shameless person.

38
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:24,839
How could I dare compare to you?

39
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:28,160
You...

40
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:29,959
You...

41
00:04:29,959 --> 00:04:30,879
You're talking nonsense!

42
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:33,319
I'm not the one saying it.

43
00:04:33,319 --> 00:04:34,360
That's just what I've heard.

44
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:36,439
They all call you, what was it...

45
00:04:37,439 --> 00:04:39,079
the one taking his sister's Medicine Holder spot,

46
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:42,720
that little good-for-nothing.

47
00:04:44,839 --> 00:04:46,360
You...

48
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:49,040
Who are you calling a good-for-nothing?

49
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:50,279
Your skin's so thick

50
00:04:50,279 --> 00:04:51,240
you can't even breathe, can you?

51
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:53,240
Too thick to breathe.

52
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:53,800
Here.

53
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:55,000
Let me give you some more.

54
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,439
Here.

55
00:04:56,439 --> 00:04:57,199
You...

56
00:04:57,199 --> 00:04:58,480
Here.

57
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:58,959
Don't be shy.

58
00:04:58,959 --> 00:04:59,879
Here.

59
00:04:59,879 --> 00:05:00,759
Who are you calling a good-for-nothing?

60
00:05:00,759 --> 00:05:02,319
Who are you calling a good-for-nothing?

61
00:05:02,319 --> 00:05:03,720
He started it!

62
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:04,759
That's clearly against the rules.

63
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:29,319
Tanxiang was right after all.

64
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:31,759
Prideful and quick to anger.

65
00:05:31,759 --> 00:05:32,800
He just can't take being provoked.

66
00:05:50,879 --> 00:05:53,120
A useless wretch who only ruins things.

67
00:05:55,199 --> 00:05:55,920
Father.

68
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:02,160
Why are you spying on Yunfan?

69
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:08,680
"Yunfan"?

70
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:10,920
Sounds awfully intimate.

71
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:13,600
Forgot your engagement to the Li family?

72
00:06:14,759 --> 00:06:16,519
Father, I didn't.

73
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,319
He's just a friend.

74
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:19,920
Enough!

75
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:22,879
Don't think I don't know he's Wuming.

76
00:06:22,879 --> 00:06:24,959
You got him into the Premier Pharmacy.

77
00:06:24,959 --> 00:06:26,800
Li Xiangyang already complained to me.

78
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,360
What?

79
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:32,279
Are you trying to anger the Li family

80
00:06:32,279 --> 00:06:33,240
and get us kicked out of the Society?

81
00:06:34,519 --> 00:06:35,560
Don't forget,

82
00:06:36,399 --> 00:06:38,399
the Lu family has made it this far

83
00:06:38,399 --> 00:06:39,560
thanks to the Li family.

84
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:46,319
As long as we can heal and save lives,

85
00:06:46,319 --> 00:06:47,959
nothing else matters.

86
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,920
Truly worthy of being

87
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:52,480
my chosen Medicine Holder prospect.

88
00:06:57,160 --> 00:06:58,000
Father,

89
00:06:58,639 --> 00:07:01,040
Mingcheng is already a Medicine Holder,

90
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:03,680
and my medical skills aren't bad either.

91
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:07,040
If promoted at the Medicine King Ceremony,

92
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:09,680
maybe our family won't need this marriage.

93
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:10,639
Insolent fool!

94
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:14,600
Do I need a worthless girl lecturing me?

95
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:17,959
What spell did that boy put on you?

96
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:20,040
Look at me.

97
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:23,800
Your only value to the Lu family

98
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:25,879
is marrying Li Xiangyang.

99
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:34,319
You think Wuming is some decent fellow?

100
00:07:34,319 --> 00:07:35,360
Let me tell you,

101
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:37,120
he's actually that Number Zero thief.

102
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:41,519
He latched onto Ye Qingxue at the Premier Pharmacy.

103
00:07:41,519 --> 00:07:45,000
Now even Song Ci has been drawn to him,

104
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:47,439
volunteering to be his Examiner.

105
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:49,360
Look at yourself.

106
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:50,600
Just look at you.

107
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:53,199
What's a minor pharmacist like you to him?

108
00:08:07,199 --> 00:08:09,600
Big sis will examine you personally.

109
00:08:11,319 --> 00:08:12,959
In all these years,

110
00:08:12,959 --> 00:08:14,920
you're the only one to get such treatment.

111
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,240
What do you mean?

112
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:24,480
Don't be shy.

113
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:28,160
This test is on body control and awareness.

114
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:32,320
We'll be having more intimate contact soon.

115
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:33,919
More intimate?

116
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:35,399
That's really not necessary.

117
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:03,159
Take off your clothes.

118
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:08,399
Why do you keep wanting me to strip?

119
00:09:08,399 --> 00:09:09,879
I'm not taking them off.

120
00:09:10,159 --> 00:09:12,279
This round is a new employee perk.

121
00:09:12,279 --> 00:09:13,879
Everyone gets it.

122
00:09:13,879 --> 00:09:14,799
Can I skip this perk?

123
00:09:14,799 --> 00:09:16,120
Hey, boss.

124
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:17,919
Is everything set up?

125
00:09:17,919 --> 00:09:19,240
It's all arranged.

126
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:21,120
Just waiting for that kid to slip up.

127
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:30,159
I'm the Deputy Medicine Overseer of Mystic Water Hall.

128
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:33,080
My technique is excellent.

129
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:35,919
Sis, I can't handle this level of intimacy.

130
00:09:35,919 --> 00:09:37,639
If you don't try something new,

131
00:09:37,639 --> 00:09:39,360
how will you know if you like it?

132
00:09:42,360 --> 00:09:43,759
Just relax.

133
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:45,399
It's only a massage.

134
00:09:45,799 --> 00:09:47,039
It's not torture.

135
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:48,320
Hold on.

136
00:09:49,120 --> 00:09:49,919
That incense...

137
00:09:49,919 --> 00:09:50,720
What did you burn?

138
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:02,720
All ready.

139
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:04,120
Wait a second.

140
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,879
I haven't agreed yet.

141
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:08,759
Then I'm going to start.

142
00:10:33,879 --> 00:10:35,360
Your acupoints here are blocked,

143
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:36,519
your qi and blood aren't flowing.

144
00:10:37,519 --> 00:10:39,480
No wonder you get tired so easily.

145
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:45,639
If it flows, there's no pain.

146
00:10:45,639 --> 00:10:46,879
If there's pain, it's blocked.

147
00:10:47,600 --> 00:10:48,879
Just bear with it for a bit.

148
00:10:50,759 --> 00:10:51,759
Little brother,

149
00:10:51,759 --> 00:10:53,759
you're yelling so loud.

150
00:10:53,759 --> 00:10:55,440
It makes it hard for me to explain.

151
00:10:57,279 --> 00:10:58,000
This isn't

152
00:10:58,600 --> 00:10:59,320
a massage.

153
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:01,519
This is straight-up torture!

154
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:06,840
What the hell do you want?

155
00:11:22,399 --> 00:11:23,039
Yunfan.

156
00:11:28,879 --> 00:11:30,000
Deputy Medicine Overseer Song.

157
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:33,679
That last test,

158
00:11:33,679 --> 00:11:34,440
you passed.

159
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:38,000
What do you mean?

160
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:39,879
I passed just like that?

161
00:11:40,879 --> 00:11:43,480
Did you think I was taking advantage of you?

162
00:11:45,799 --> 00:11:48,360
This is Mystic Water Hall's exclusive trial.

163
00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:50,200
Meridian examination.

164
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:52,480
Those who stay conscious under my pressure

165
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:53,919
are quite rare.

166
00:11:53,919 --> 00:11:55,919
What, you want to continue?

167
00:11:57,159 --> 00:11:57,840
No thanks.

168
00:11:58,919 --> 00:12:00,279
Farewell. Goodbye.

169
00:12:00,600 --> 00:12:01,120
Yunfan.

170
00:12:01,919 --> 00:12:03,159
Tanxiang, run!

171
00:12:03,159 --> 00:12:03,879
Watch out!

172
00:12:03,879 --> 00:12:05,440
There's still the next round.

173
00:12:16,799 --> 00:12:17,919
This third floor

174
00:12:17,919 --> 00:12:19,919
is the core medicinal bath area of Mystic Water Hall.

175
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:22,240
It's usually open to patients too.

176
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:24,039
Mainly for physical recovery and therapy.

177
00:12:24,919 --> 00:12:25,919
I thought

178
00:12:25,919 --> 00:12:28,519
Mystic Water Hall only handled logistics and HR.

179
00:12:28,519 --> 00:12:30,039
Didn't expect you to have some skills.

180
00:12:30,799 --> 00:12:33,559
Hydrotherapy is a secret art of Mystic Water Hall.

181
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:36,440
Each of these springs has a unique effect.

182
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:39,320
Many formulas are exclusive secret recipes.

183
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:42,000
Nice.

184
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:43,720
Impressive.

185
00:12:45,639 --> 00:12:46,559
So what's this spring?

186
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:49,480
This is the Nine-Cycle Soul-Returning Spring.

187
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:50,799
It treats reverse meridian damage.

188
00:12:53,440 --> 00:12:55,279
It feels like thousands of needles piercing bone,

189
00:12:55,279 --> 00:12:56,240
agonizing to the core.

190
00:12:57,879 --> 00:13:00,480
But it can quickly repair the meridians.

191
00:13:00,480 --> 00:13:02,320
This isn't a spring soak,

192
00:13:02,879 --> 00:13:04,080
this is straight-up torture.

193
00:13:04,799 --> 00:13:06,240
There's more above.

194
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:08,080
This is the Hundred Flowers Beauty Spring.

195
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:09,840
After soaking, the skin becomes like jade,

196
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:11,000
with a rosy complexion.

197
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:12,639
It's a favorite among female guests.

198
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:18,480
Alright.

199
00:13:19,120 --> 00:13:21,480
Up ahead is our medicinal bath trial area.

200
00:13:27,679 --> 00:13:29,000
What's this one?

201
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:29,799
Forgiveness Spring.

202
00:13:29,799 --> 00:13:31,360
This is the Mint Cooling Spring.

203
00:13:31,799 --> 00:13:33,840
Soaking eliminates fatigue,

204
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:34,799
refreshes and clears the mind.

205
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:37,919
Quite a variety, I'll give you that.

206
00:13:37,919 --> 00:13:38,919
But who knows

207
00:13:38,919 --> 00:13:40,759
if the effects match the advertising.

208
00:13:43,919 --> 00:13:45,720
Look at you, acting so inexperienced.

209
00:13:49,960 --> 00:13:51,720
Well, if it isn't my defeated foe,

210
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:52,399
Medicine Holder Lu.

211
00:13:52,799 --> 00:13:53,360
What did you say?

212
00:13:53,879 --> 00:13:55,200
Who's your defeated foe?

213
00:13:55,919 --> 00:13:57,799
You sneaky scoundrel set me up earlier.

214
00:13:58,440 --> 00:14:00,000
You can't go around saying that.

215
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:03,440
Deputy Medicine Overseer Song supervised personally.

216
00:14:03,440 --> 00:14:04,200
What do you mean by that?

217
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:05,480
That because of her oversight,

218
00:14:05,480 --> 00:14:06,639
you were able to set me up?

219
00:14:06,639 --> 00:14:07,679
I did not.

220
00:14:11,159 --> 00:14:12,639
I doubt your dumb luck will hold forever.

221
00:14:15,399 --> 00:14:17,240
This round, the medicinal bath trial

222
00:14:17,240 --> 00:14:19,279
tests the candidate's diagnostic ability

223
00:14:19,279 --> 00:14:20,840
and precision in formulating the bath.

224
00:14:20,840 --> 00:14:22,600
Candidates must, within an hour,

225
00:14:22,600 --> 00:14:24,000
based on their own constitution,

226
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:25,799
prepare a suitable medicinal bath

227
00:14:25,799 --> 00:14:27,600
and personally enter the pool to test it.

228
00:14:28,279 --> 00:14:30,200
Soaking yourself, huh?

229
00:14:30,639 --> 00:14:31,440
Interesting.

230
00:14:32,200 --> 00:14:34,440
Alright, you may begin selecting herbs.

231
00:14:43,519 --> 00:14:44,919
What are you spacing out for?

232
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:49,440
Don't forget Father's instructions.

233
00:14:50,440 --> 00:14:51,120
Go.

234
00:15:00,399 --> 00:15:02,000
For the medicinal bath round,

235
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:03,799
while Yang Yunfan is picking his herbs,

236
00:15:03,799 --> 00:15:04,759
take this

237
00:15:04,759 --> 00:15:06,200
and slip it into his bath.
